casebody.data:
Lyman et al. v. Stephenson. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 3, 1890.) Appeal from special term.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

J. N. Hayes, for appellant. F. T. Murphy, for respondents.

No opinion. Motion to dismiss appeal denied, and case struck off calendar.
